oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A Rational basis for the prevention of parturient paresis
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Mayer, G. P.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: parturient paresis
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Although several regimes have been reported which successfully reduce the incidence of parturient paresis, a program which is both universally acceptable and successful has not yet emerged. In this paper fundamental aspects of the syndrome will be discussed aiming to improve management practices through a better understanding of the basic processes involved in the disease
